{"tid":2152950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指黎智英案由警方國安處調查　未有交駐港國安公署","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:11:04.000Z","uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"da39c84473f1c8bc1d54fd675ac6333f14293fb0","tid":2152950,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:19:13.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒的創辦人黎智英與多名高層，以及前香港眾志成員周庭等共10人，分別涉嫌違反《港區國安法》與串謀欺詐被捕，全部獲准保釋候查，9月上旬向警方報到。消息指，案件繼續由警方國安處調查，未有交由駐港國安公署處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，黎智英助手Mark Simon及「我要攬炒」團隊成員劉祖迪亦被通緝，涉嫌勾結境外勢力。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，黎智英以30萬元現金及20萬元人事擔保保釋外出，警方凍結他的5000萬元資產，其他被捕人士則獲准以2萬至10萬元現金保釋，另加人事擔保，所有人要交出旅遊證件。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報道，黎智英中午返回壹傳媒大樓，他下午向員工表示，希望員工不要因為大批警員進入大樓而害怕，如果害怕就是中計，又說對市民及員工的支持感動，如果早知道有今日，他都不會改變。"},{"pid":"73fb3d3b68b8ac114c9315821d1cafbb35d087ba","tid":2152950,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1543321_1_L_20200812170416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1543321_1_L_20200812170416.jpg&h=a73566da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e292cb4beeb7555102f40f09b6be3f2af9fd54","tid":2152950,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"警方凍結他的5000萬元資產  CLS"},{"pid":"7e2ed9f77f43f1dadd7f2021ef35cac3da6c69cd","tid":2152950,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"根本個駐港國安公署就得個樣嚇9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6e96269318b8313e1dd60e5c3cd04e2cab9e8b","tid":2152950,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2ed9f77f43f1dadd7f2021ef35cac3da6c69cd","tid":2152950,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor